        unify(y, x + n);
        if (find(x) == find(y)) return false;
    }
    return true;
}
```
The nodes that dislike the nodes that we dislike (NDND).

The nutshell of the idea above is that we cannot connect to nodes that we dislike, but we can connect to NDND. The only problem is that we don't know NDND beforehand, so to trick the system we create complementary nodes that are already NDND and connect to them without any shame.

