	colour   -1 -1 -1 -1

	queue : 1

	from adjacency list for node = 1
	index     1  2  3  4
	colour    1 -1 -1 -1

	then add all 1's adjacent nodes into queue and pop 1

	queue : 2,3

	for 2,   colour[2] = 1-colour[curr] (here colour[2] = 1 - 1 = 0) (here curr is from which node 2 is inserted means here it is 1)
	index     1  2  3  4
