**Synopsis:**

Track each customer's wait time based upon the `last` customer's job completion time and the current customer's job start time `i` and job length `j`.  Return the average wait time, ie. the accumulated sum of `wait` times divided by the cardinality of the `wait` times.

---

**Bi-Weekly Contest 42 Screenshare:**

![image](https://assets.leetcode.com/users/images/39e17532-4994-4600-9fbc-baf4a2585828_1609000229.6503932.png)

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=h5V7ybR-vps

