*Kotlin*
```
class Solution {
    fun averageWaitingTime(A: Array<IntArray>): Double {
        var time = 0
        var last = 0
        var wait = mutableListOf<Double>()
        A.forEach { (i, j) ->
            time = Math.max(i, last)
            last = time + j
            wait.add(last - i.toDouble())
        }
        return wait.sum() / wait.size
    }
}
```

*Javascript*
